{
  "stem": "24130.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was so happy that I gave her some water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, they closed the trains again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were going and going and going on this train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and then, all of a sudden, somebody came out-- was standing near the window and says, you know, we just passed the-- the-- the-- the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We're already in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They saw the Polish stations, the names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- now, my father says we lost.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He gave us always hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he just felt that if we're in Poland, that's the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he-- he took us together, the sisters and my brothers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said to us, you remember for-- I had $600 that I-- I had for the boat, the ticket.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't give the $600 when they-- we came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I have that money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And everybody has some money in their coat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he did it on his own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He put in in the-- in the shoulder pad, he put in some money for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He says, a-- an American dollar is always good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If you could buy yourself some bread, if you could run away, if you could do something, you have some money with you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But he says, you should try everything to survive if you can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But he says, if you have to die, [SOBBING] you should know that you're dying, because you Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You're not dying that you did something wrong, only because you're Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There are bad people that chose to be bad, to kill Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But he says, if you could save yourself, you should do everything in your power to survive and to continue to be Jewish and to continue the-- the life that we-- I started you out with.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
